enter of the wheel tell you exactly when to up- or down-shift. You maintain maximum acceleration without taking your eyes off the track. A 24-point selection dial and the +/- buttons on the front of the wheel let you further fine-tune your driving preferences.";s:10:"post_title";s:26:"Logitech G29 DRIVING FORCE";s:12:"post_excerpt";s:44:"<small>Brand - LOGITECH Color - BLUE</small>";s:11:"post_status";s:7:"publish";s:14:"comment_status";s:4:"open";s:11:"ping_status";s:6:"closed";s:13:"post_password";s:0:"";s:9:"post_name";s:26:"logitech-g29-driving-force";s:7:"to_ping";s:0:"";s:6:"pinged";s:0:"";s:13:"post_modified";s:19:"2019-10-04 09:49:29";s:17:"post_modified_gmt";s:19:"2019-10-04 06:49:29";s:21:"post_content_filtered";s:0:"";s:11:"post_parent";s:1:"0";s:4:"guid";s:51:"https://wisaki.co.ke/?post_type=product&#038;p=8614";s:10:"menu_order";s:1:"0";s:9:"post_type";s:7:"product";s:14:"post_mime_type";s:0:"";s:13:"comment_count";s:1:"0";}}